    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Twitter share and facebook like button for <code>html/erb</code>
```html</p>

<div class='spread'>
  <div class='twshare left'>
    <a href="http://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-count="horizontal" data-via="funonrails">Tweet</a><script type="text/javascript" src="http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js"></script>
  </div>
  <script src="http://connect.facebook.net/en_US/all.js#xfbml=1"></script><fb:like href="" layout="button_count" show_faces="false" width="450" font=""></fb:like>
</div>


<p>```</p>

<p>Twitter share and facebook like button for <code>haml</code>
```haml
.spread
  .twshare.left</p>

<pre><code>%a.twitter-share-button.left{"data-count" =&gt; "horizontal", "data-via" =&gt; "fuonrails", :href =&gt; "http://twitter.com/share"} Tweet
%script{:src =&gt; "http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js", :type =&gt; "text/javascript"}
</code></pre>

<p>  .fshare.left{:style => &lsquo;padding-left: 0px; margin-left: 10px;&rsquo;}</p>

<pre><code>%script{:src =&gt; "http://connect.facebook.net/en_US/all.js#xfbml=1"}
%fb:like{:layout =&gt; "button_count", :show_faces =&gt; "false", :width =&gt; "450"}
</code></pre>

<p>  .CLR
```</p>

